# MONEY::NETWORK_SPEND_EARNED_FROM_BANK_AND_WALLETS

## Summary
Deduct the given amount as earned vc (EVC) from the bank and all character wallets

## Parameters
* **INT** amount

## Returns
* **INT**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Hardcoded to return 0.
